  {
    "row": 161,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## ローカルGradioデモ"
  },
  {
    "row": 162,
    "rowsha": "UwpVmtj7AXoMSDrlnL1QfsiduHqUQu2gaj4LhFsaR8o=",
    "originContent": "## Local Gradio Demo",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 163,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "インタラクティブなテストのためのGradioベースのウェブUIも提供しています。ブラシで領域をなぞり、参照画像をアップロードし、すべての推論パラメータをブラウザ上で調整できます。"
  },
  {
    "row": 164,
    "rowsha": "1sKG8mwp4NISC+17t/+h/7Ca5aqa0xLvAEa7ZaMcn4I=",
    "originContent": "We also provide a Gradio-based web UI for interactive testing. You can brush regions, upload reference images, and adjust all inference parameters in the browser.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 165,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 166,
    "rowsha": "rTMjNc+qNIxb1xXDR5hEYiJw1fc4muBwuBsTXVIaIho=",
    "originContent": "```bash",
    "translatedContent": "```bash"
  },
  {
    "row": 167,
    "rowsha": "yTP73cr3O39gKLRUBLHoG37pGRVYjUGUDuod1taGRp8=",
    "originContent": "python app.py",
    "translatedContent": "python app.py"
  },
  {
    "row": 168,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 169,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 170,
    "rowsha": "TFOHrWslMDenKGe36ne1oiek8LNTtRmcMr7iJfBrCI8=",
    "originContent": "Then open `http://localhost:7860` in your browser. The app will automatically download the base model (`Qwen/Qwen-Image-Edit-2511`) and the RefineAnything LoRA from Hugging Face on first launch.",
    "translatedContent": "次に、ブラウザで `http://localhost:7860` を開きます。アプリは初回起動時にベースモデル（`Qwen/Qwen-Image-Edit-2511`）とRefineAnything LoRAをHugging Faceから自動的にダウンロードします。"
  },
  {
    "row": 171,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 172,
    "rowsha": "BiJ61vSbajzldbz4FIJCFowD/Yr1PqQ4d/ZROZxs+CY=",
    "originContent": "You can specify a custom base model path via the `MODEL_DIR` environment variable:",
    "translatedContent": "`MODEL_DIR` 環境変数を使ってカスタムベースモデルのパスを指定できます："
  },
  {
    "row": 173,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 174,
    "rowsha": "rTMjNc+qNIxb1xXDR5hEYiJw1fc4muBwuBsTXVIaIho=",
    "originContent": "```bash",
    "translatedContent": "```bash"
  },
  {
    "row": 175,
    "rowsha": "qPqB8SkdITmfNmzadHQgTse60sVd51iGjQfLGLrysEo=",
    "originContent": "MODEL_DIR=/path/to/local/Qwen-Image-Edit-2511 python app.py",
    "translatedContent": "MODEL_DIR=/path/to/local/Qwen-Image-Edit-2511 python app.py"
  },
  {
    "row": 176,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 177,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 178,
    "rowsha": "D/TFBPjveucOoqUdIpXORIVFV6LRCLc3DkQyxbj4T/M=",
    "originContent": "**Features of the Gradio demo:**",
    "translatedContent": "**Gradioデモの特徴：**"
  },
  {
    "row": 179,
    "rowsha": "EN6irNL6H4HVCn+BzwYojyTmT8YlBG9Pomp9Tzx0lhE=",
    "originContent": "- **Brush-to-select**: paint directly on the source image to define the refinement region.",
    "translatedContent": "- **ブラシで選択**：元画像に直接ペイントしてリファインメント領域を定義します。"
  },
  {
    "row": 180,
    "rowsha": "EBkG7jqDHvtbVi/RJA01fsqOoFfPJ9+NorIfU26ycDc=",
    "originContent": "- **Optional reference image**: upload a second image and optionally brush to crop a specific reference area.",
    "translatedContent": "- **オプションの参照画像**：2枚目の画像をアップロードし、必要に応じてブラシで特定の参照領域を切り取れます。"
  },
  {
    "row": 181,
    "rowsha": "IZcjd5857e/X7/6A3M/NXenfgk0BTDlsLg9CfvkYA8I=",
    "originContent": "- **Focus crop**: automatically crops and zooms into the edit region for higher detail fidelity, then composites back seamlessly.",
    "translatedContent": "- **フォーカスクロップ**：編集領域を自動でクロップおよびズームし、高精細で処理後にシームレスに合成します。"
  },
  {
    "row": 182,
    "rowsha": "7krXrlGqTbLD5mYxIRcT5rNFw3wLjC5BTd9sA0tNhv4=",
    "originContent": "- **Lightning LoRA**: one-click toggle for faster inference with fewer steps.",
    "translatedContent": "- **Lightning LoRA**：ステップ数を減らした高速推論をワンクリックで切り替え可能。"
  },
  {
    "row": 183,
    "rowsha": "EyMoy2yiVl+ACSTy58zxW8nZrhUAxhNj2TOPcG7Ldnk=",
    "originContent": "- **Before / After slider**: instantly compare input and output.",
    "translatedContent": "- **ビフォー／アフタースライダー**：入力と出力を即座に比較可能。"
  },
  {
    "row": 184,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
